feat(trip-ai): 新增仪表盘图片AI识别并回填耗油记录 | Add dashboard image AI extraction and auto-fill trip records

- 类型(Type): feat, service, refactor, ui, docs
- 功能(Feature): 在耗油记录页新增仪表盘图片上传与AI识别入口，自动提取平均油耗与行驶距离并回填表单。
- 服务(Service): 后端新增 /api/trip/ai-extract 与 /uploads/* 图片访问能力，支持调用 OpenAI 识别并保存图片路径返回前端。
- 重构(Refactor): 扩展 TripRecord 与 store 清洗/新增/更新链路，统一持久化 dashboardImagePath/dashboardImageUrl 字段并兼容旧数据。
- 交互与界面(UI/UX): 增加图片预览、识别状态提示、历史与详情页图片查看入口，保持移动端可读性。
- 文档(Docs): 更新 README、backend README 与 .env 示例，补充 AI 识别环境变量与接口说明。

- Types: feat, service, refactor, ui, docs
- Feature: Added dashboard image upload and AI extraction entry in trip page to auto-fill average fuel consumption and distance fields.
- Service: Added backend /api/trip/ai-extract and /uploads/* handlers to call OpenAI, persist uploaded image, and return structured output.
- Refactor: Extended TripRecord and store sanitize/create/update pipeline to persist dashboardImagePath/dashboardImageUrl with backward compatibility.
- UI/UX: Added image preview, extraction status feedback, and image access points in trip history/detail views with mobile readability preserved.
- Docs: Updated README, backend README, and .env examples with AI extraction env vars and API contract.
